item.title: Doing Everything
item.description: 16-year old Jerry is obsessed with his 11-year old sister Ashley, as is their step-father. What Jerry sees while peeping on his kid sister today changes both of their lives for the better.

item.title: The Red Rooster
item.description: 'I marveled at her lithe little body, tall and oh so thin; she somehow managed to combine the carefree ease of childhood, the hesitating awkwardness of adolescence, and just a little hint of the graceful beauty of womanhood. A perfect filly, Ellie May was.' The hero, an unemployed lawyer in town to adjudicate the estate of a deceased relative, stumbles upon a small town's, and his relative's, dark secret. In the process he falls head-over-heels in love. And, I suppose it goes without saying, has lots of graphic sex with underage girls.

item.title: Kira
item.description: A man falls head-over-heels in love with a 14-year-old girl and they have a brief sexual relationship; she returns at 17 to live with him and his new wife as a boarder. Plenty of mushy love but even more sloppy sex! Hope you like it.

item.title: Molly and the Babysitting Advert
item.description: A naive teenager falls prey to an evil paedophile. Initially being forced so comes to start to realise her place and enjoys it.

item.title: Perverted Parenting
item.description: A little girl's life of sexual abuse changes for the better after she is filmed being molested by two women and her daddy. Rewritten for Loliwood Studios.
